  "technicalDetails": "vCard (RFC 6350 for v4.0, RFC 2426 for v3.0) is a text-based contact information format. Each property is a line with NAME;PARAMS:VALUE syntax. Version 2.1 uses QP encoding; 3.0 uses Base64 for binary data; 4.0 supports URI references and richer media types. Multiple vCards can be concatenated in a single file.",
  "completenessScore": 88
